# NativeWind / Tailwind (Inversora)

Expo SDK 57 app with **NativeWind v4** hybrid styling. Default to `className`; use `StyleSheet` only on precision-native surfaces.

## Default workflow

1. Style static layout with semantic Tailwind classes: `bg-surface`, `text-text-secondary`, `gap-md`, `rounded-card`, `shadow-card`, `p-md`.
2. Compose with `cn()` from `@/shared/utils/cn`.
3. Map variants through `src/shared/nativewind/theme-classes.ts` (`typographyClassNames`, `themeColorClassNames`, button/card variants).
4. Use `useTheme()` from `@/shared/hooks/use-theme` for third-party APIs (`MaterialCommunityIcons` `color`, `TextInput`, charts, SVG).

## Do not

- Do not default to `StyleSheet.create` for new visual UI (conflicts with the hybrid model).
- Do not use arbitrary hex in components (`bg-[#fff]`); use semantic tokens.
- Do not use `dark:` or system color scheme â€” MVP is light only (`userInterfaceStyle: light`).
- Do not put `className` on `Animated.Text` or Reanimated-driven text (ellipsis/alignment break on native).
- Do not add `StyleSheet` outside the whitelist without updating docs + `stylesheet-whitelist.ts`.

## StyleSheet whitelist

Precision components keep layout/animation in `StyleSheet` or inline `style`:

- Canonical list: `src/shared/nativewind/stylesheet-whitelist.ts`
- Human doc: `docs/architecture/tailwind-stylesheet-whitelist.md`
- Exceptions catalog: `docs/architecture/styling-exceptions.md`

When using non-obvious `style`/`StyleSheet`, add `// tailwind-exception: <reason>`.

Register new whitelist entries in the same PR (code + docs).

## Token pipeline (single source of truth)

| Change | Run |
|--------|-----|
| Palette/spacing JSON or semantic colors | `pnpm run generate:theme` |
| Output files | `src/global.css`, `tailwind.config.js` (generated â€” do not hand-edit) |

Primitives: `src/shared/theme/palette.primitives.json`, `spacing.primitives.json`.  
Runtime theme: `src/shared/theme/colors.ts`, `tokens.ts`.

## Build wiring

| File | Role |
|------|------|
| `babel.config.js` | `nativewind/babel` + `jsxImportSource: 'nativewind'` |
| `metro.config.js` | `withNativeWind({ input: './src/global.css' })` + React dedupe for pnpm |
| `nativewind-env.d.ts` | `/// <reference types="nativewind/types" />` |
| `src/app/_layout.tsx` | `import '@/global.css'` + `import '@/shared/nativewind/css-interop'` |
| `src/app/+html.tsx` | `import '@/global.css'` for web SSR |
| `src/shared/nativewind/css-interop.ts` | `cssInterop` for `Image`, `LinearGradient` |

## Reuse before creating UI

Follow `.cursor/rules/ux-system-reuse.mdc` â€” prefer `@/shared/components/ui/*` with `className` tokens.

